    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable dings and some paint fading on the hood and roof, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, but it will likely need some routine maintenance, such as new brake pads and a suspension check, in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of character and potential DIY projects.",
