    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, providing a comfortable and dependable driving experience. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, though you may find some minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age. On the exterior, the paint still retains a nice shine, with only a few small stone chips and light surface scratches visible upon close inspection. All major systems, including the air conditioning and electronics, are fully functional. It\u2019s a solid, road-ready car that offers great value for anyone seeking a balance of quality and longevity.",
