    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a true museum-grade example, preserved in a climate-controlled environment and presenting as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior features original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like finish, entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Every body panel is laser-straight with perfect factory gaps and untouched trim. Inside, the cabin is a pristine time capsule; the premium leather remains supple with zero bolster wear, and the dashboard is flawless without a single UV-related blemish. All electronic components, from the precision gauges to the original audio system, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a fully documented service history that reflects meticulous, proactive maintenance. The engine bay is show-ready, showing no signs of fluid seepage or corrosion. This vehicle includes all original manuals, a complete set of keys, and a comprehensive folder of maintenance receipts. For the discerning collector seeking a turn-key, flawless specimen, this is an unrivaled opportunity.",
